"title": "8760: fools, characteristics of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8760",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture portrays fools as those who have rejected God and his ways and are unable or unwilling to appreciate the wisdom of knowing and obeying him.</p>\n<h2>The world regards Christians as fools</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:10\">1CO 4:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:26-1Cor1:31\">1CO 1:26–1:31</a></p>\n<h2>The world regards the gospel as foolish</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:18\">1CO 1:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:20-1Cor1:25\">1CO 1:20–1:25</a></p>\n<h2>Fools do not believe in God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps53:1\">PSA 53:1</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps14:1\">PSA 14:1</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:21\">ROM 1:21</a></p>\n<h3>Fools do not trust God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos7:11\">HOS 7:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:7-2Chr16:9\">2CH 16:7–16:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa19:11-Isa19:13\">ISA 19:11–19:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:1\">ISA 30:1</a></p>\n<h3>Fools lack knowledge of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:22\">JER 4:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:4\">JER 5:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:21\">JER 5:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps92:6\">PSA 92:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:25\">LUK 24:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:15-Eph5:17\">EPH 5:15–5:17</a></p>\n<h2>The behaviour of fools</h2>\n<h3>Fools worship idols</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:8\">JER 10:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:14\">JER 10:14</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:17\">JER 51:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:22-Rom1:23\">ROM 1:22–1:23</a></p>\n<h3>Fools act in a godless manner</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa32:6\">ISA 32:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps94:5-Ps94:8\">PSA 94:5–94:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:23\">PRO 10:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl7:25\">ECC 7:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:22\">JER 4:22</a></p>\n<h3>Fools are dishonest</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:11\">JER 17:11</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Fools give vent to their anger</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:11\">PRO 29:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl7:9\">ECC 7:9</a></p>\n<h3>Fools are disobedient</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam13:13\">1SA 13:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam24:10\">2SA 24:10</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr21:8\">1CH 21:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:17\">PSA 107:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:8\">PRO 10:8</a></p>\n<h3>Fools despise instruction and discipline</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:22\">PRO 1:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:28-Prov1:33\">PRO 1:28–1:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov5:23\">PRO 5:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:15\">PRO 12:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:2\">ISA 65:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer18:12\">JER 18:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:7\">EZK 3:7</a></p>\n<h2>The speech of fools</h2>\n<h3>Fools speak unwisely</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:6-Prov18:7\">PRO 18:6–18:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl10:12\">ECC 10:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:4\">EPH 5:4</a></p>\n<h3>Fools are slanderous</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:18\">PRO 10:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:15\">2PE 2:15</a></p>\n<h3>Fools are mockers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:9\">PRO 14:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:22\">PRO 1:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:6\">PRO 14:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:9\">PRO 23:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:9\">PRO 24:9</a></p>\n<h3>Fools love quarrelling and dissension</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:3\">PRO 20:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:1\">PRO 19:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:4\">1TI 1:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:4\">1TI 6:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:23\">2TI 2:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:9\">TIT 3:9</a></p>\n<h3>The words of fools are empty</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:2\">PRO 15:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:7\">PRO 14:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:7\">PRO 26:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:17\">ECC 9:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl10:14\">ECC 10:14</a></p>\n<h2>Fools rely on themselves</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:15\">PRO 12:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:12\">PRO 14:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:26\">PRO 28:26</a></p>\n<h2>Fools rely on words, not deeds</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:20\">JAS 2:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:4\">ECC 5:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:39-Luke11:40\">LUK 11:39–11:40</a></p>",
